            "text": " **Remark 1.1.** We see that Conjecture B implies Conjecture A by setting  $A_1 = H$ ,  $B_1 = gH$ ,  $C_1 = g^2H$ ,  $A_2 = g^3H$ ,  $B_2 = g^4H$ ,  $C_2 = g^5H$ ,..., $A_e = g^{3e-3}H$ ,  $B_e = g^{3e-2}H$  and  $C_e = g^{3e-1}H$  where  $e = \\left\\lfloor\\frac{\\ell_0}{3}\\right\\rfloor$ . Moreover, Conjecture B does not assume that  $4 \\nmid o_p(2)$ .",
